      <title>英国央行贝利谈降息、通胀和英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/boe-s-bailey-on-rate-cut-inflation-and-the-pound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利表示，“不要指望利率回到零”，他解释了央行为何自 2020 年初以来首次降息。周四，他与弗朗辛·拉夸进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/boe-s-bailey-on-rate-cut-inflation-and-the-pound</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:59:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国航空母公司再次放弃收购欧洲航空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/iag-drops-plan-to-buy-air-europa-after-regulator-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国航空公司 (British Airways) 母公司 IAG SA 表示，由于发现监管机构的反对意见无法提供完成交易的可行途径，该公司将放弃收购西班牙航空公司欧罗巴航空 (Air Europa) 的计划，这是该公司第二次试图收购这家西班牙航空公司，但未能成功。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/iag-drops-plan-to-buy-air-europa-after-regulator-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:54:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能可前石油主管亿万富翁被指控腐败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/glencore-s-billionaire-ex-oil-head-alex-beard-charged-with-corruption-by-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc) 前石油主管、亿万富翁亚历克斯·比尔德 (Alex Beard) 以及该大宗商品交易商的其他四名前雇员被英国最高反欺诈机构指控犯有腐败罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/glencore-s-billionaire-ex-oil-head-alex-beard-charged-with-corruption-by-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 14:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员充分预期美联储今年将降息三次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bond-traders-are-fully-pricing-in-three-fed-rate-cuts-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府债券在经历了今年最好的月份之后进一步上涨，因为经济数据被视为巩固美联储今年三次降息的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bond-traders-are-fully-pricing-in-three-fed-rate-cuts-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 14:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>价格风险掩盖经济增长放缓 捷克放缓降息步伐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/czechs-slow-rate-cuts-as-inflation-risks-trump-sluggish-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于持续的价格压力和克朗贬值掩盖了支持缓慢经济复苏的需要，捷克央行放缓了货币宽松步伐。克朗上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/czechs-slow-rate-cuts-as-inflation-risks-trump-sluggish-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 12:31:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约养老金本财年上涨 10%，超过目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/new-york-city-pensions-gain-10-in-fiscal-year-beating-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市的五家养老金机构在上个财年大幅超额完成了投资目标，并有望因美国股市上涨而为纽约市节省数亿美元的缴费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/new-york-city-pensions-gain-10-in-fiscal-year-beating-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市下跌，法国CAC 40指数进入回调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/european-stocks-edge-lower-after-glum-results-from-autos-socgen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一系列令人失望的收益和疲软的美国数据引发了人们对整体经济健康状况的担忧，欧洲股市下跌。法国 CAC 40 指数进入技术性回调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/european-stocks-edge-lower-after-glum-results-from-autos-socgen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安赛乐米塔尔对中国钢铁出口表示不满</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/arcelormittal-cries-foul-on-china-steel-exports-as-profit-falls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安赛乐米塔尔公司 (ArcelorMittal SA) 表示，中国的出口已使钢铁市场陷入“难以持续”的境地，该公司报告季度利润出现下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/arcelormittal-cries-foul-on-china-steel-exports-as-profit-falls</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:10:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求担忧抑制中东局势升级 油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济放缓的迹象抵消了对中东冲突可能危及供应的担忧，油价在创下九个多月来最大涨幅后回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 23:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：‘经济警告’导致美国债券收益率下降，股市受创</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[疲软的经济数据引发市场对美联储等待太长时间才开始降息的担忧，导致债券价格上涨，而股市受到打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 22:40:30 GMT</pubDate>
